87
00:07:46,674 --> 00:07:49,886
Hei! Minum, minum!

88
00:07:49,969 --> 00:07:52,054
Minum, minum!

89
00:07:52,138 --> 00:07:54,015
Minum, minum!

90
00:07:54,098 --> 00:07:56,309
- Cepat minumlah.
- Minum, minum!

91
00:07:57,101 --> 00:07:59,645
- Wah, dia minum.
- Dia minum.

92
00:07:59,729 --> 00:08:00,730
Bagus sekali.

93
00:08:01,355 --> 00:08:04,484
Jangan diminum sekaligus.
Kau bisa mabuk.

94
00:08:08,446 --> 00:08:10,364
Aku sudah memanggil Yong-su.

95
00:08:10,448 --> 00:08:12,825
- Yong-su?
- Sialan.

96
00:08:13,367 --> 00:08:14,327
Maaf.

97
00:08:15,703 --> 00:08:18,414
Sungguh? Yong-su sangat tampan.

98
00:08:18,498 --> 00:08:20,458
- Kau suka semua pria.
- Sial.

99
00:08:51,447 --> 00:08:52,615
Kenapa kau di luar?

100
00:08:54,951 --> 00:08:56,661
- Kau baik-baik saja?
- Apa?

101
00:08:58,037 --> 00:08:59,413
Ah, aku baik-baik saja.

102
00:08:59,497 --> 00:09:01,666
Sudah kubilang, minumlah perlahan.

103
00:09:02,583 --> 00:09:04,710
Aku sungguh baik-baik saja.

104
00:09:05,294 --> 00:09:06,128
Syukurlah.

105
00:09:08,172 --> 00:09:09,382
Hei, Chun-ae.

106
00:09:12,134 --> 00:09:13,010
Ya?

107
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:17,682
Ada yang ingin kukatakan.

108
00:09:20,142 --> 00:09:23,396
<i>Hatiku bergetar</i>

109
00:09:23,896 --> 00:09:29,443
<i>Kau ambil seluruh hatiku</i>

110
00:09:30,444 --> 00:09:32,113
Apa aku boleh meminjam uang?

111
00:09:34,615 --> 00:09:35,533
Apa?

112
00:09:35,616 --> 00:09:38,536
Aku harus membayar lebih dari perkiraanku.

113
00:09:40,121 --> 00:09:41,789
Berapa banyak?

114
00:09:42,373 --> 00:09:43,624
Sekitar 200,000 won.

115
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,669
