Apa?

197
00:15:15,706 --> 00:15:17,708
Kim Chun-ae, kelas 10-2 SMA Seongil.

198
00:15:24,173 --> 00:15:27,217
<i>Aku merasa tatapannya padaku
sangat berbeda.</i>

199
00:15:28,093 --> 00:15:29,637
<i>Itu memberiku kesenangan.</i>

200
00:15:44,985 --> 00:15:46,528
Ah, astaga.

201
00:15:47,613 --> 00:15:49,823
Kau mengejutkanku. Pergilah.

202
00:15:57,206 --> 00:15:58,999
Bangunlah. Ayo makan.

