00:17:03,605 --> 00:17:04,440
Bisa menari?

220
00:17:05,107 --> 00:17:07,651
- Aku penari di acara promosi.
- Wah, bagus.

221
00:17:08,819 --> 00:17:10,904
Kau tak akan terlalu banyak disentuh.

222
00:17:10,988 --> 00:17:14,366
Namun, mungkin ada orang
yang sedikit menyentuhmu.

223
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:15,451
Hindari mereka.

224
00:17:16,243 --> 00:17:19,288
Di sini, tidak banyak
pelanggan yang suka menyentuh.

225
00:17:20,289 --> 00:17:23,792
